<div id="review_1862536321" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1862536321" />
    <a title="Kathleen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39134508-kathleen"><img alt="Kathleen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1495314753p2/39134508.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1862536321?book_show_action=true">Nov 26, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathleen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathleen" href="/user/show/39134508-kathleen">Kathleen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1862536321" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13846636654858182249">Pat Conroy (1945-2016) was one of America&apos;s most acclaimed and widely read authors and the New York Times-bestselling writer of eleven novels and memoirs. <br/>Although a fictional novel, Pat Conroy&apos;s writing was heavily influenced by his personal life experiences. <br/>THE GREAT SANTINI depicts a Marine Corps pilot who is a domineering father often physically and emotionally abusive to his children. This is an intense, dramatic, passionate and sometimes humorous read. It was made into a major film. <br/>4 sta</span>
  <span id="freeText13846636654858182249" style="display:none">Pat Conroy (1945-2016) was one of America's most acclaimed and widely read authors and the New York Times-bestselling writer of eleven novels and memoirs. <br />Although a fictional novel, Pat Conroy's writing was heavily influenced by his personal life experiences. <br />THE GREAT SANTINI depicts a Marine Corps pilot who is a domineering father often physically and emotionally abusive to his children. This is an intense, dramatic, passionate and sometimes humorous read. It was made into a major film. <br />4 stars</span>
  <a data-text-id="13846636654858182249" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


