<div id="review_20926478" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/20926478" />
    <a title="Marguerite" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1038238-marguerite"><img alt="Marguerite" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1223735807p2/1038238.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/20926478?book_show_action=true">Apr 24, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marguerite" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marguerite" href="/user/show/1038238-marguerite">Marguerite</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Brats</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1038238-marguerite?shelf=read-over-and-over">read-over-and-over</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer20926478" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2590043989335382196">I saw the movie before I read the book, and it was the first time I saw my experiences as a military brat played out in a work of fiction. I recognized the shifting family dynamics and the insistence on appearances to the exclusion of all else. I experienced the warrior culture, the comradeship of a family in opposition to the world every time we transfered, too, and moves from one alien environment to another. My dad was no Bull Meecham, but he was a piece of work. Conroy helps me remember. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


